{"tid":1568352,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"續。割蓆宣言","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T00:37:46.000Z","uid":175453,"like":70,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ebcefc821ad17bcdd9fdb37ddd80022e8d3d6b02","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"有鑑於港共同狗隻對香港人既打壓無效<br />\n極有可能出現偽裝示威者以抺黑示威者之行為<br />\n以及 現時出現了有組織性針對/攻擊年輕人的藍絲集團<br />\n為了保護示威者自身安全以及統一<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動理念</span></span><br />\n<br />\n現正作出<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">示威宣言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一，示威者不會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">惡意</span></span>傷害任何<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無辜</span></span>人士之性命財產。<br />\n<br />\n二，示威者不強姦，不搶劫。<br />\n<br />\n三，示威者對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">報導事實</span></span>的記者，醫護，外國朋友等一律表示尊重。<br />\n<br />\n四，示威者作出的一切行為㫮對準<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港共極權或任何助長港共極權之人士、團體和機構</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n一，無辜人士例子：路過市民，遊客，手足。<br />\n<br />\n二，藍絲即為助長極權人士，示威者所作的所有行動皆為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準極權</span></span>，和理手足請<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">開遮</span></span>保護。<br />\n<br />\n三，假若左膠出現，請當作有助長極權之嫌疑，請手足幫忙控制并拉其至安全區域。例如，黑警身邊，以務求讓左膠獲得黑警保護。<br />\n<br />\n五，只要不違反以上行動理念，則<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勿捉鬼</span></span>。例如，你懷疑某人身分，但其行動與理念一致，則不用再懷疑，以免重犯14年錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n六，若有文宣巴絲認為言之有理，請幫忙翻譯為英文并向外宣傳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上PO:<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"8244fcca7700eedef39b9147f5a4515ddd05517d","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"此為後續更新資訊樓"},{"pid":"b94a1e530888bfeb5ceae5b1738f7d97c453777c","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"f8e64b2d10c810f6a98ef20ae9bdc098659b7101","tid":1568352,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13129084e4a282b062dd4e16e25f9df733d2966a","tid":1568352,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fae3ec501666c85a839e57246c66350dd970986b","tid":1568352,"uid":310898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"冇嘢需要討論，和理非好明白勇武做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n勇武知道底線 <br />\n<br />\n和勇一家、無分彼此，互相合作先會見到勝利<br />\n<br />\n大家都明白嘅道理，希望大家繼續秉持<br />\n<br />\n光復香港、時代革命<br />\n<br />\n9.15見"},{"pid":"1d04e1c760163b1dd0071e5ee6facb64562cb47c","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇左四"},{"pid":"1d9c60526d360b229dd14ca077539f2663250d7c","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8244fcca7700eedef39b9147f5a4515ddd05517d","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"此為後續更新資訊樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"同為手足當然理解所說理念 但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外人</span></span>或跟得唔貼既就未必 所以必須宣傳"},{"pid":"887a741f39c48a3664ead4a3e137ef637cd8ce32","tid":1568352,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:29:16.